                    <h2>Jos Poortvliet</h2>
                    <h3>Nextcloud</h3>
                    <p>People person, technology enthusiast and all-things-open evangelist. I have managed and marketed communities for over a decade, getting started in the KDE community, followed by working as openSUSE Community Manager at SUSE and ownCloud. Currently I take care of communication and marketing at Nextcloud. I am busy growing the Nextcloud community, speaking at and organizing conferences and writing about my passions ranging from psychology and people in communities to innovative technology.</p>
